data.description: Welcome to your spacious and unique three bed, two bath home with a flair for individuality. This is not your cookie-cutter floorplan. As you step inside, you're greeted by a main hallway with the formal dining room on the left, graced by a stylish single bypass barn door that adds a touch of rustic charm and separates this space for special occasions. On the right, you'll find a versatile flex room. Whether you envision a second living area, home theater, or perhaps a fourth bedroom, this space adapts to your needs. The heart of the home boasts a generously sized living area, and adjacent to it, the well-appointed kitchen with modern appliances, ample counter space, and a cozy breakfast nook?the perfect spot for morning coffee or casual meals. Retreat to the primary suite, which is a private haven featuring an en-suite bathroom with dual sinks, soaking tub, and separate shower. Two more large bedrooms ensure plenty of space for family and guests. Rounding out the amazing feature list in this home is the spacious, three-car garage, covered back porch and fully-fenced backyard for unwinding after a long day. Book your exclusive tour today!
